anda tidak mempunyai tanda penyesalan atau renungan.

64
00:04:24,514 --> 00:04:25,473
Anda layak untuk mati!

65
00:04:32,272 --> 00:04:33,690
Di manakah dia berada?

66
00:04:35,191 --> 00:04:36,943
MIN SOHEE

67
00:04:37,026 --> 00:04:40,113
Kapten, mereka akan melalui Persimpangan Gahan di jalan lingkar luar.

68
00:04:40,196 --> 00:04:41,114
Baik.

69
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:43,825
Jungsub…

70
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:48,746
CHA YEONHO

71
00:04:52,917 --> 00:04:54,669
 <b>- Tuan.</b>  <b>- Yeonho.</b>

72
00:04:55,878 --> 00:04:57,714
Saya akan bawa Pyo Myunghak bersama saya.

73
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:00,049
Kita mesti singkirkan dia

74
